#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:1
msgid "Environment Variables"
msgstr "环境变量"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:3
msgid ""
"Below are some environment variables that can be set, along with their "
"descriptions. All of the MagiAttention-specific ones are prefixed with "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_`."
msgstr "以下是一些可以设置的环境变量及其说明。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:7
msgid ""
"Since MagiAttention is actively evolving, many advanced but experimental "
"features will be released but enabled through environment variables."
msgstr "由于 MagiAttention 正在积极发展中，许多高级但实验性的功能将通过环境变量启用后发布。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:15
msgid "For Correctness"
msgstr "正确性相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:17
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:19
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:36
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:113
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:125
