#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:420
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:441
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:460
msgid "**Defaults to:** `0`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `0`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:20
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_fwd_high_precision_reduce_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_fwd_high_precision_reduce_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:22
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable high-precision (fp32) reduce "
"for partial out during dist-attn forward to trade-off double comm "
"overhead for increased precision and less dtype-cast overhead."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 dist-attn 前向传播中 partial out "
"的高精度（fp32）reduce，以双倍通信开销换取更高精度和更少的 dtype 转换开销。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:26
msgid ""
"Inside the ffa forward kernel, we always use high-precision (fp32) "
"accumulation for partial out."
msgstr "在 ffa 前向内核内部，我们始终对 partial out 使用高精度（fp32）累加。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:28
msgid "We always use high-precision (fp32) lse everywhere."
msgstr "我们在所有地方始终使用高精度（fp32）的 lse。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:30
msgid "This feature works for out only when enabling qo comm."
msgstr "此功能仅在启用 qo comm 时对 out 生效。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:34
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BACKWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BACKWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:37
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_bwd_high_precision_reduce_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_bwd_high_precision_reduce_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:39
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable high-precision (fp32) reduce "
"for partial dq,dk,dv during dist-attn backward to trade-off double comm "
"overhead for increased precision and less dtype-cast overhead."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 dist-attn 反向传播中 partial dq,dk,dv "
"的高精度（fp32）reduce，以双倍通信开销换取更高精度和更少的 dtype 转换开销。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:43
msgid ""
"Inside the ffa backward kernel, we always use high-precision (fp32) "
"accumulation for partial dq,dk,dv."
msgstr "在 ffa 反向内核内部，我们始终对 partial dq,dk,dv 使用高精度（fp32）累加。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:45
msgid "This feature works for dq only when enabling qo comm."
msgstr "此功能仅在启用 qo comm 时对 dq 生效。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:49
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:51
msgid "**Defaults to:** `none` (options: `none`, `sum`, `avg`)"
msgstr "**默认值：** `none`（可选值：`none`、`sum`、`avg`）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:52
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.dsink_all_reduce_op`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.dsink_all_reduce_op`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:54
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the all-reduce op for sink "
"gradients within `dist_attn_func` when involving attention sink."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制涉及 attention sink 时 `dist_attn_func` 中 sink 梯度的 all-reduce 操作。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:58
msgid ""
"For now we only accept global replicated sink tensor as input to feed "
"into `dist_attn_func`, and the gradients of sink in each cp rank are "
"partial and requires to be sum-reduced across cp ranks."
msgstr ""
"目前我们仅接受全局复制的 sink 张量作为输入传入 `dist_attn_func`，每个 cp rank 中的 sink 梯度是部分的，需要在"
" cp rank 之间进行 sum-reduce。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:60
msgid ""
"However, since sink tensor is learnable, it will be considered as a "
"regular parameter in the model similar to `bias` in `nn.Linear` layer."
msgstr "然而，由于 sink 张量是可学习的，它将被视为模型中的常规参数，类似于 `nn.Linear` 层中的 `bias`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:62
msgid ""
"So under some popular training frameworks, such as Megatron-LM, FSDP, the"
" sum-reduction across cp ranks of the partial gradients of sink might be "
"automatically applied within the whole `dp x cp` mesh."
msgstr ""
"因此在一些流行的训练框架（如 Megatron-LM、FSDP）中，sink 部分梯度在 cp rank 之间的 sum-reduction "
"可能会在整个 `dp x cp` mesh 中自动执行。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:64
msgid ""
"To avoid repeated reduction, we provide this environment variable to "
"specify the all-reduce op for sink gradients within `dist_attn_func`, "
"whose default value is `none` to NOT apply any reduction to sink "
"gradients by `dist_attn_func` and let the framework handle it."
msgstr ""
"为避免重复 reduction，我们提供此环境变量来指定 `dist_attn_func` 中 sink 梯度的 all-reduce "
"操作，其默认值为 `none`，即 `dist_attn_func` 不对 sink 梯度执行任何 reduction，而由框架来处理。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:66
msgid ""
"However, under the scenarios w/o any framework mechanism to reduce "
"parameters across cp ranks, you have to specify this environment variable"
" to `sum`."
msgstr "但在没有任何框架机制来跨 cp rank reduce 参数的场景下，您必须将此环境变量设为 `sum`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:68
msgid ""
"And sometimes, `avg` might also be an option when you need to scale the "
"sink gradients by `1/cp`."
msgstr "有时 `avg` 也是一个选项，当您需要将 sink 梯度按 `1/cp` 缩放时可以使用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:72
msgid "For Runtime"
msgstr "运行时相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:74
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_LOG_LEVEL**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_LOG_LEVEL**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:76
msgid "**Defaults to:** `WARN`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `WARN`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:77
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.log_level`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.log_level`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:79
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to control the logging verbosity of the entire "
"`magi_attention` package. Valid values (case-insensitive) are `DEBUG`, "
"`INFO`, `WARN`, `WARNING`, `ERROR`, `CRITICAL`."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量以控制整个 `magi_attention` 包的日志详细程度。有效值（不区分大小写）为 "
"`DEBUG`、`INFO`、`WARN`、`WARNING`、`ERROR`、`CRITICAL`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:82
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:84
msgid "**Defaults to:** `ffa`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `ffa`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:85
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:114
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:271
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.kernel_backend`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.kernel_backend`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:87
msgid "Set this env variable to choose the attn kernel backend. Valid values are:"
msgstr "设置此环境变量以选择注意力内核后端。有效值为："

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:89
msgid "`ffa`: flex-flash-attention (default, high-performance persistent kernel)."
msgstr "`ffa`：flex-flash-attention（默认，高性能持久化内核）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:90
msgid ""
"`sdpa`: offline SDPA implementation (for testing / high precision like "
"`fp32`/`fp64`)."
msgstr "`sdpa`：离线 SDPA 实现（用于测试 / `fp32`、`fp64` 等高精度）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:91
msgid ""
"`sdpa_ol`: online (block-wise) SDPA implementation (for testing, lower "
"memory than `sdpa`)."
msgstr "`sdpa_ol`：在线（分块）SDPA 实现（用于测试，显存占用低于 `sdpa`）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:92
msgid "`fa4`: Flash-Attention 4 monkey-patch (workaround for Blackwell GPUs)."
msgstr "`fa4`：Flash-Attention 4 monkey patch（Blackwell GPU 的临时方案）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:95
msgid ""
"This supersedes the legacy `MAGI_ATTENTION_SDPA_BACKEND=1` and "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_FA4_BACKEND=1` toggles, which are still supported but "
"must NOT be set together with `MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND`."
msgstr ""
"此变量取代了旧的 `MAGI_ATTENTION_SDPA_BACKEND=1` 和 `MAGI_ATTENTION_FA4_BACKEND=1`"
" 开关，后者仍受支持，但不得与 `MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND` 同时设置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:99
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PRECISION**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PRECISION**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:101
msgid "**Defaults to:** unset (use the input dtype as-is)"
msgstr "**默认值：** 未设置（保持输入 dtype 不变）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:102
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.precision`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.precision`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:104
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to override the compute dtype for attention "
"kernels. Valid values are `bf16`, `fp16`, `fp32`, `fp64`. When set, input"
" Q/K/V are cast to the specified dtype before attention computation, and "
"the output is cast back to the original input dtype."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量以覆盖注意力内核的计算 dtype。有效值为 `bf16`、`fp16`、`fp32`、`fp64`。设置后，输入 Q/K/V "
"会在注意力计算前转换为指定 dtype，输出再转换回原始输入 dtype。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:109
msgid "For Performance"
msgstr "性能相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:111
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FA4_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FA4_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:116
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to switch the attn kernel backend from "
"`FFA` to `FFA_FA4`, a monkey patch version of Flash-Attention 4, to "
"temporarily support arbitrary mask on Blackwell GPUs."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以将注意力内核后端从 `FFA` 切换到 `FFA_FA4`——Flash-Attention 4 的 monkey"
" patch 版本，以临时支持 Blackwell GPU 上的任意掩码。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:119
msgid ""
"This is a legacy toggle kept for backward compatibility; prefer "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND=fa4`. This is for now a workaround "
"solution might be removed or updated in the future."
msgstr ""
"这是为向后兼容保留的旧开关；推荐使用 "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND=fa4`。这目前是一个临时解决方案，未来可能会被移除或更新。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:123
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_NATIVE_GRPCOLL**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_NATIVE_GRPCOLL**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:126
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_native_grpcoll_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_native_grpcoll_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:128
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable native kernel implementation "
"for group collective comm."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 group collective 通信的原生内核实现。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:131
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:143
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:155
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now, and "
"not compatible with many other features, thus please do NOT enable it "
"unless you know exactly what you are doing."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中，与许多其他功能不兼容，因此请不要启用，除非您清楚了解其影响。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:135
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_QO_COMM**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_QO_COMM**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:138
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_qo_comm_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_qo_comm_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:140
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable query/output communication, "
"including fetching remote q (fwd), reducing partial out and lse (fwd), "
"fetching remote q,o,lse,do (bwd), reducing partial dq (bwd), to eliminate"
" the restriction that communication is limited solely to key/value."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 query/output 通信，包括获取远程 q（前向）、reduce partial out 和 "
"lse（前向）、获取远程 q,o,lse,do（反向）、reduce partial dq（反向），以消除通信仅限于 key/value 的限制。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:147
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FLATTEN_HEAD_GROUPS**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FLATTEN_HEAD_GROUPS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:150
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.is_flatten_head_groups_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_flatten_head_groups_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:152
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to flatten head groups within GQA/MQA "
"attention to optimize dynamic solver performance."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以展平 GQA/MQA attention 中的 head groups 来优化 dynamic solver 性能。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:159
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_AUTO_RANGE_MERGE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_AUTO_RANGE_MERGE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:162
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.is_auto_range_merge_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_auto_range_merge_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:164
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable automatic range merging for "
"flex-flash-attention, to improve performance by reducing the number of "
"attention ranges."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以启用 flex-flash-attention 的自动范围合并，通过减少注意力范围的数量来提升性能。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:168
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:180
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now, thus "
"please do NOT enable it unless you know exactly what you are doing."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中，因此请不要启用，除非您清楚了解其影响。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:172
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CATGQA**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CATGQA**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:175
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.is_cat_gqa_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_cat_gqa_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:177
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable CatGQA mode for flex-flash-"
"attention backward, to further optimize the performance under GQA "
"settings by concatenating multiple Q heads sharing the same KV head."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以启用 flex-flash-attention 反向的 CatGQA 模式，通过拼接共享相同 KV head "
"的多个 Q head 来进一步优化 GQA 设置下的性能。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:184
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BWD_HIDE_TAIL_REDUCE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BWD_HIDE_TAIL_REDUCE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:187
msgid ""
"**Used by:** "
"`magi_attention.env.general.dist_attn_backward_hide_tail_reduce`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.dist_attn_backward_hide_tail_reduce`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:189
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to trade saving the last remote `kv` "
"activation for reordering overlap stages during backward, hiding the "
"final remote `group_reduce` with the host FFA stage."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以牺牲保存最后一个远程 `kv` 激活来重排反向传播中的重叠阶段，将最终的远程 `group_reduce` "
"隐藏在主机 FFA 阶段中。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:192
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now, and "
"not compatible with many other features like qo comm, thus please do NOT "
"enable it unless you know exactly what you are doing."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中，与许多其他功能（如 qo comm）不兼容，因此请不要启用，除非您清楚了解其影响。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:196
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_MIN_CHUNKS_PER_RANK**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_MIN_CHUNKS_PER_RANK**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:198
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:249
msgid "**Defaults to:** `8`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `8`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:199
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.min_chunks_per_rank`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.min_chunks_per_rank`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:201
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the minimum number of "
"chunks per context parallel rank, to control the granularity of "
"computational load-balance."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制每个上下文并行 rank 的最小 chunk 数量，从而控制计算负载均衡的粒度。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:203
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FORWARD_SM_MARGIN**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FORWARD_SM_MARGIN**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:205
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:212
msgid "**Defaults to:** `4` if `CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS` > `1`, otherwise `0`"
msgstr "**默认值：** 当 `CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS` > `1` 时为 `4`，否则为 `0`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:206
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.ffa_fwd_sm_margin_save_for_comm`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.ffa_fwd_sm_margin_save_for_comm`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:208
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of SMs of the "
"ffa forward kernel saved for comm kernels."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制 ffa 前向内核为通信内核预留的 SM 数量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:210
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_BACKWARD_SM_MARGIN**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_BACKWARD_SM_MARGIN**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:213
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.ffa_bwd_sm_margin_save_for_comm`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.ffa_bwd_sm_margin_save_for_comm`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:215
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of SMs of the "
"ffa backward kernel saved for comm kernels."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制 ffa 反向内核为通信内核预留的 SM 数量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:217
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CPP_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CPP_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:220
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.is_cpp_backend_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_cpp_backend_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:222
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable C++ backend for core data "
"structures (`AttnRange`, `AttnMaskType`, etc.) to avoid Python overhead."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用核心数据结构（`AttnRange`、`AttnMaskType` 等）的 C++ 后端，以避免 Python "
"开销。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:225
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now. If the"
" C++ extension is not found or this variable is set to `0`, it will fall "
"back to the Python implementation."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中。如果未找到 C++ 扩展或此变量设为 `0`，将回退到 Python 实现。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:229
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_HIERARCHICAL_COMM**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_HIERARCHICAL_COMM**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:232
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_hierarchical_comm_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_hierarchical_comm_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:234
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable hierarchical group-collective "
"comm within 2-dim cp group (inter_node group + intra_node group)."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用二维 cp group（inter_node group + intra_node group）内的分层 "
"group-collective 通信。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:237
msgid ""
"This is for now a temporary solution to reduce the redundant inter-node "
"communication and might be removed or updated in the future."
msgstr "这目前是减少冗余节点间通信的临时方案，未来可能会被移除或更新。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:240
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DIST_ATTN_RUNTIME_DICT_SIZE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DIST_ATTN_RUNTIME_DICT_SIZE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:242
msgid "**Defaults to:** `1000`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `1000`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:243
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.dist_attn_runtime_dict_size`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.dist_attn_runtime_dict_size`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:245
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the maximum LRU cache size "
"of `dist_attn_runtime_dict_mgr`."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制 `dist_attn_runtime_dict_mgr` 的最大 LRU 缓存大小。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:247
msgid "**CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS**"
msgstr "**CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:250
msgid ""
"**Used by:** "
"`magi_attention.env.general.is_cuda_device_max_connections_one`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_cuda_device_max_connections_one`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:252
msgid ""
"This environment variable defines the number of hardware queues that CUDA"
" streams can utilize. Increasing this value can improve the overlap of "
"communication and computation, but may also increase PCIe traffic."
msgstr "此环境变量定义了 CUDA stream 可以使用的硬件队列数量。增大此值可以改善通信与计算的重叠，但也可能增加 PCIe 流量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:255
msgid "For Debug"
msgstr "调试相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:257
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SANITY_CHECK**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SANITY_CHECK**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:260
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.is_sanity_check_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_sanity_check_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:262
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable many sanity check codes inside "
"magi_attention."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 magi_attention 内部的大量健全性检查代码。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:265
msgid ""
"This is only supposed to be used for testing or debugging, since the "
"extra sanity-check overhead might be non-negligible."
msgstr "此功能仅用于测试或调试，因为额外的健全性检查开销可能不容忽视。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:268
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SDPA_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SDPA_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:273
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` can switch the attn kernel backend from "
"ffa to sdpa-math, to support higher precision like `fp32` or `fp64`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 可将注意力内核后端从 ffa 切换到 sdpa-math，以支持更高精度（如 `fp32` 或 `fp64`）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:276
msgid ""
"This is a legacy toggle kept for backward compatibility; prefer "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND=sdpa`. This is only supposed to be used "
"for testing or debugging, since the performance is not acceptable."
msgstr ""
"这是为向后兼容保留的旧开关；推荐使用 "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND=sdpa`。此功能仅用于测试或调试，因为其性能不可接受。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:280
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DETERMINISTIC_MODE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DETERMINISTIC_MODE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:283
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.is_deterministic_mode_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_deterministic_mode_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:285
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable deterministic mode to use "
"deterministic algorithms for all magi_attention kernels."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用确定性模式，对所有 magi_attention 内核使用确定性算法。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:288
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PROFILE_MODE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PROFILE_MODE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:291
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.is_profile_mode_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_profile_mode_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:293
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable profiling mode to profile all "
"magi_attention kernels, currently mainly for ffa kernels (*see "
"[here](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/exps/attn/profile_ffa) for more details*)."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用性能分析模式，对所有 magi_attention 内核进行性能分析，目前主要针对 ffa "
"内核（*详情请参阅[此处](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/exps/attn/profile_ffa)*）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:296
msgid ""
"This is only supposed to be used for development. Please do NOT enable it"
" in production."
msgstr "此功能仅用于开发，请勿在生产环境中启用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:299
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_CUTEDSL_DEBUG_MODE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_CUTEDSL_DEBUG_MODE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:302
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.kernel.cutedsl`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.kernel.cutedsl`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:304
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable debug-time checks and "
"diagnostics for the CuteDSL FFA kernels."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以为 CuteDSL FFA 内核启用调试期检查和诊断。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:306
msgid "For Build"
msgstr "构建相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:308
msgid "JIT"
msgstr "JIT"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:310
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_WORKSPACE_BASE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_WORKSPACE_BASE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:312
msgid "**Defaults to:** `$HOME`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `$HOME`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:313
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.build.workspace_base_dir`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.build.workspace_base_dir`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:315
msgid ""
"Specifies the base directory for the MagiAttention workspace, which "
"includes cache and generated source files."
msgstr "指定 MagiAttention 工作空间的基础目录，包含缓存和生成的源文件。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:317
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_VERBOSE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_VERBOSE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:320
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.build.is_build_verbose`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.build.is_build_verbose`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:322
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable verbose output during the JIT "
"compilation process, showing the full ninja build commands being "
"executed."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 JIT 编译过程中的详细输出，显示正在执行的完整 ninja 构建命令。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:324
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_DEBUG**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_DEBUG**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:327
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.build.is_build_debug`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.build.is_build_debug`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:329
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable debug flags for the C++/CUDA "
"compiler. This includes options like `-g` (debugging symbols) and other "
"flags to get more detailed information, such as register usage."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 C++/CUDA 编译器的调试标志。这包括 "
"`-g`（调试符号）等选项和其他用于获取更详细信息（如寄存器使用情况）的标志。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:331
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_NO_BUILD_CACHE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_NO_BUILD_CACHE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:334
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.build.is_no_build_cache`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.build.is_no_build_cache`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:336
msgid "Toggle this env variable to `1` to disable caching for built ffa kernels."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以禁用已构建 ffa 内核的缓存。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:338
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORCE_JIT_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORCE_JIT_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:341
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.build.is_force_jit_build`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.build.is_force_jit_build`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:343
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to force building FFA in JIT mode, even "
"the pre-built AOT `libs` exists."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以强制以 JIT 模式构建 FFA，即使预构建的 AOT `libs` 已存在。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:345
msgid "**NVCC_THREADS**"
msgstr "**NVCC_THREADS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:347
msgid "**Defaults to:** `4`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `4`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:348
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.build.nvcc_threads`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.build.nvcc_threads`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:350
msgid ""
"Sets the number of threads for `nvcc`'s `--split-compile` option, which "
"can speed up the JIT compilation of CUDA kernels."
msgstr "设置 `nvcc` 的 `--split-compile` 选项的线程数，可加速 CUDA 内核的 JIT 编译。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:352
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_CUTEDSL_CACHE_ENABLED**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_CUTEDSL_CACHE_ENABLED**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:355
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:362
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.kernel.cutedsl.cache_utils`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.kernel.cutedsl.cache_utils`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:357
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable on-disk caching of compiled "
"CuteDSL FFA kernels."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用已编译 CuteDSL FFA 内核的磁盘缓存。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:359
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_CUTEDSL_CACHE_DIR**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_CUTEDSL_CACHE_DIR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:361
msgid "**Defaults to:** unset (use the default cache location)"
msgstr "**默认值：** 未设置（使用默认缓存位置）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:364
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to specify the directory for the CuteDSL FFA kernel"
" cache."
msgstr "设置此环境变量以指定 CuteDSL FFA 内核缓存的目录。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:367
msgid "AOT"
msgstr "AOT"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:369
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA_JOBS**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA_JOBS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:371
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:378
msgid "**Defaults to:** `ceil(num_cpu_cores * 0.9)`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `ceil(num_cpu_cores * 0.9)`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:372
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:379
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:386
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:393
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:400
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:407
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:414
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:421
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:435
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:442
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:449
msgid "**Used by:** `setup.py`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `setup.py`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:374
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of parallel "
"compilation jobs used to pre-build ffa kernels."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制预构建 ffa 内核时使用的并行编译任务数。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:376
msgid "**MAX_JOBS**"
msgstr "**MAX_JOBS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:381
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of parallel "
"compilation jobs used to build the extension modules other than ffa."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制构建 ffa 以外的扩展模块时使用的并行编译任务数。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:383
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:385
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:467
msgid "**Defaults to:** `1`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `1`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:388
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable pre-build ffa kernels for some "
"common options with `ref_block_size=None` and leave others built in jit "
"mode."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用对一些 `ref_block_size=None` 的常见选项预构建 ffa 内核，其余选项则以 JIT 模式构建。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:390
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_CUDA_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_CUDA_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:395
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to skip building all the CUDA extension "
"modules entirely (e.g. for a Python-only / docs build)."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以完全跳过构建所有 CUDA 扩展模块（例如仅 Python / 文档构建时）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:397
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_EXT_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_EXT_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:402
msgid "Toggle this env variable to `1` can skip building `magi_attn_ext`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 可跳过构建 `magi_attn_ext`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:404
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_COMM_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_COMM_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:409
msgid "Toggle this env variable to `1` can skip building `magi_attn_comm`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 可跳过构建 `magi_attn_comm`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:411
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORCE_CXX11_ABI**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORCE_CXX11_ABI**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:416
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to force building the extension modules "
"with the C++11 ABI (`_GLIBCXX_USE_CXX11_ABI=1`), to match a PyTorch build"
" compiled with the new ABI."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以强制使用 C++11 ABI（`_GLIBCXX_USE_CXX11_ABI=1`）构建扩展模块，以匹配使用新 ABI"
" 编译的 PyTorch。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:418
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DISABLE_SM90_FEATURES**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DISABLE_SM90_FEATURES**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:423
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to disable the SM90 (Hopper)-specific "
"features when building the extension modules, e.g. when targeting a "
"toolchain without SM90 support."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以在构建扩展模块时禁用 SM90（Hopper）专属特性，例如面向不支持 SM90 的工具链时。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:425
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FA4_CACHE_DIR**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FA4_CACHE_DIR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:427
msgid "**Defaults to:** `magi_attention/lib/ffa_fa4_cache/`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `magi_attention/lib/ffa_fa4_cache/`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:428
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.functional.fa4_utils`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.functional.fa4_utils`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:430
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to specify the cache directory for pre-compiled "
"`FFA_FA4` kernels."
msgstr "设置此环境变量以指定预编译 `FFA_FA4` 内核的缓存目录。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:432
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:434
msgid "**Defaults to:** unset (auto-detect the current GPU device)"
msgstr "**默认值：** 未设置（自动检测当前 GPU 设备）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:437
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to specify the compute capability used to build "
"MagiAttention extension modules (affects `magi_attn_comm` and "
"`create_block_mask`). Supports comma-separated values for multi-arch "
"builds, e.g. `MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY=90,100`. If not "
"set, we will try to detect the compute capability of the current GPU "
"device, and raise an error if detection fails."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量以指定构建 MagiAttention 扩展模块时使用的计算能力（影响 `magi_attn_comm` 和 "
"`create_block_mask`）。支持逗号分隔的多架构值，例如 "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY=90,100`。如果未设置，我们将尝试检测当前 GPU "
"设备的计算能力。如果检测失败将抛出错误。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:439
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_ALLOW_BUILD_WITH_CUDA12**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_ALLOW_BUILD_WITH_CUDA12**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:444
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to `1` to allow building MagiAttention extension "
"modules with `CUDA-12`, which might cause significant performance "
"degradation compared to `CUDA-13+`. When `0`, we will raise an error and "
"abort the installation if the CUDA version is lower than `13.0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以允许使用 `CUDA-12` 构建 MagiAttention 扩展模块，这可能导致与 `CUDA-13+` "
"相比显著的性能下降。当为 `0` 时，如果 CUDA 版本低于 `13.0`，我们将抛出错误并中止安装。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:446
msgid "**NVSHMEM_DIR**"
msgstr "**NVSHMEM_DIR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:448
msgid ""
"**Defaults to:** the system module `nvidia-nvshmem-cu12` (as listed in "
"`requirements.txt`)"
msgstr "**默认值：** 系统模块 `nvidia-nvshmem-cu12`（如 `requirements.txt` 中所列）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:451
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to the path of the custom `nvshmem` installation "
"directory."
msgstr "设置此环境变量为自定义 `nvshmem` 安装目录的路径。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:453
msgid ""
"If not found anywhere, all relative features used in native group "
"collective comm kernels are disabled."
msgstr "如果在任何位置都未找到，native group collective 通信内核中的所有相关功能将被禁用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:456
msgid "For Testing"
msgstr "测试相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:458
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PARAMETERIZE_RUN_IN_MP**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PARAMETERIZE_RUN_IN_MP**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:461
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.testing` (`with_run_in_mp`)"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.testing` (`with_run_in_mp`)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:463
msgid ""
"Whether to run parameterized distributed test cases in a multiprocessing "
"context. This is set internally by the `@with_run_in_mp` decorator rather"
" than being configured by users directly."
msgstr "是否在多进程上下文中运行参数化的分布式测试用例。此变量由 `@with_run_in_mp` 装饰器内部设置，而非由用户直接配置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:465
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_TEST_PRINT_NO_MISMATCH**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_TEST_PRINT_NO_MISMATCH**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:468
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.testing` (`assert_close`)"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.testing` (`assert_close`)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:470
msgid ""
"Whether to print the \"has no mismatch\" message when two tensors match "
"in `assert_close`. Set to `0` to disable it, mainly used to reduce "
"logging noise in CI."
msgstr ""
"当两个张量在 `assert_close` 中匹配时，是否打印 “has no mismatch” 消息。设为 `0` "
"可禁用它，主要用于减少 CI 中的日志噪声。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:472
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_COPYRIGHT_TEST_YEAR**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_COPYRIGHT_TEST_YEAR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:474
msgid "**Defaults to:** current calendar year"
msgstr "**默认值：** 当前日历年份"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:475
msgid "**Used by:** `tools/codestyle/copyright.py`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `tools/codestyle/copyright.py`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:477
msgid ""
"Overrides the \"current year\" used by the copyright-header check. Useful"
" for reproducible testing of the copyright tooling."
msgstr "覆盖版权头检查所使用的“当前年份”。用于对版权工具进行可复现的测试。"
